### HEALTH (quick sanity)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

### REGISTER (ALL FIELDS REQUIRED)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "yacine",
  "email": "yacine@test.com",
  "password": "Secret123!",
  "fullName": "Yacine Bouziane",
  "age": 29,
  "height": 174,
  "weight": 77,
  "dailyCalorieGoal": 2400,
  "targetWeight": 82
}

### REGISTER (NEGATIVE: missing a field → 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "yacine2",
  "email": "yacine2@test.com",
  "password": "Secret123!",
  "fullName": "Y B",
  "age": 29,
  "height": 174,
  "weight": 77,
  "dailyCalorieGoal": 2400
  // "targetWeight" missing
}

