### LOGIN (success)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "yacine",
  "password": "Secret123!"
}

### LOGIN (NEGATIVE: bad password → 401)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "yacine",
  "password": "WrongPass!"
}

### ME (works only when cookie is set by login/register)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me

### UPDATE PROFILE (ALL FIELDS REQUIRED)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Yacine B.",
  "age": 30,
  "height": 175,
  "weight": 78,
  "dailyCalorieGoal": 2300,
  "targetWeight": 82
}

### UPDATE PROFILE (NEGATIVE: missing a field → 400)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Missing Field Demo",
  "age": 30,
  "height": 175,
  "weight": 78,
  "dailyCalorieGoal": 2300
  // targetWeight missing
}

### CHANGE PASSWORD (success)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Secret123!",
  "newPassword": "EvenMoreSecret456!"
}

### CHANGE PASSWORD (NEGATIVE: wrong current → 400)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/change-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "not_the_right_one",
  "newPassword": "x"
}

### LOGOUT (clears cookie)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/logout

### ME after logout (NEGATIVE: should be 401)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/auth/me
